metadata.name: Meta Forest 0.2
metadata.description:
Forest with a digital experience, In future the resonance emanating from trees & augmented creatures will offer us the most surreal experience. The merge of physical & digital world will change the way we feel & interact with our environment. Meta forest portrays a complete Augmented forest that is still only an idea in 2022. 


Location - Kodaikanal, India
Size - 1920X1080 
Camera - Pocket dji 2
Software - Aftereffects, Garageband
